overview: Check it out because these girls are takin' charge like their name was Charles! We've given 6 hotties the chance to put the camera in their hands as they play with themselves...live! Who knows what tricks she'll pull when the doors are closed and the windows are shut! It's just her and the camera now and it's priceless.
tagline: A Girl And Her Camera: Priceless.
title: I Film Myself 3
